title: #4【バイオハザードre4】はじめてのバイオハザードre4やるにぇえええええええ！！！※未成年視聴注意【ホロライブ/さくらみこ】
name: Sakura Miko

entries.text: Alright everyone, it's been a little while since the last time,
but we're going to keep going with RE4 today!
It's Part 4, so this is the fourth time. Apparently, we're still in the mid-game.
Don't point that gun at me! Hahaha. Sorry, I might still be in the mindset of the last stream.
It's not like I'm losing to some small-fries. I'm directing that at those zombies and Plagas with the internal parasites.
I plan to look back at the previous stream and watch a recap clip before we start.
By the way, I did the new outfit reveal with Sui-chan yesterday, thank you very much for watching!
Also, today, I uploaded a Shorts video,
choreography for MiComet's second original song
was revealed for the first time
in that Short on Miko-chan's channel,
So please, go take a look!
It just opens on its own.
Do you guys remember the summary of the story so far?
in extremely lame ways over and over again.
It's practically love at this point.
The last stream was so dense. The story development was intense.
Okay, about 3 boss battles? Wait, 3? Wasn't it like 5?
We got stuck in the swamp quite a bit, unexpectedly.
So, I'm going to watch the recap of the previous stream with you all.
Thank you to the people making so many clips.
"Leon succeeded in rescuing the imprisoned Ashley."
"However, without time to feel relieved, a horde of enemies surrounded the pair."
"Leon attempts to protect her and escape."
This is the start of the last stream.
It's the aftermath of a death match.
It helps that this is a proper summary.
Wait, didn't I throw up too?
I threw up on the boat, didn't I?
"If it's in the early stages, it can be completely removed with surgery."
We didn't solve any of Luis's mysteries last time.
Ramon is that guy... the master.
Don't tell me he made it?
He said he was at Umbrella
With Ada, we haven't met yet.

How long has it been in the timeline?
You're strict about the details! Ada... Ada was in RE2, right?
Ada coming to save the day—so beautiful.
Wait, Ada is too erotic! Beautiful.
It's been 6 years since RE2? Wow.
I see. That backflip wasn't necessary!
They're the people on the attaché case charms.
I thought this guy was Saddler.
I really thought he was Saddler.
I was trying to be so cool...
Wait for it, the problem scene.
This was a terrible scene last time.

It was a deathmatch until I had zero healing left.
It's super cut, but I retried this about 5 times.
I bet I'll have to fight him too.
I don't want to. Ah, what's that behind him?
I wonder what the Castellan is.

I don't understand the guts here.
Ah, this is towards the end of the last stream.

Yes, so... give back the knife! The knife is gone!
Yes, so that was Sakura Miko realizing the knife was taken after the fact.
I'll be starting from the continuation of this.
Yes, thank you for the wonderful, easy-to-understand clip. Thank you, thank you.
Nice summary, thank you very much. When there's a gap in time, I forget things, so that was a good refresher.
Ah, this is the main story loading.
Ah, was this the one at the top?
"Ashley suddenly turned a blade on Leon and ran deep into the castle with unsteady steps like a puppet. Dominated by confusion and anxiety..."
"Situation critical. Took refuge in the castle but got separated from the target."
Not connecting at all. No signal?
It's not reaching. What happened to the helicopter? Did they prep the heli? Finally, Chapter 8. Hello, Miko-Leon is back after a while.
You know, can I say one thing? I get that Ashley is scared.
The fear of realizing you're turning into a monster. I understand that because I'm turning into a monster too.
I get it, but separating at this timing... I really wish she hadn't done that.
It's just my feeling, you know?
I'm fighting with my life on the line here! Heave-ho.
Okay... Right, my healing items are low right now.
"It wasn't her own will to leave." That's true, but still.
And how do these Plagas even work?
How they control people is a mystery. How do they do that?
Really? The knife? Ah, really, what about the knife?
"Looks like you're having a tough time." Ah.
Okay, save... Ah, before saving, let's do some shopping.
"Protective gear that completely blocks gunshots and explosive damage,"
"Durability lost from damage can be repaired at the shop."
This is the simple version? No, this is it.
"We also offer repair services." I'll buy a First Aid Spray too.
Blacktail... nah, I'm good. This is fine too.
I don't really need Resources (L). Let me repair this.
Ah, an indentation. An indentation for a Yellow Diamond.
It's a round indentation so the Viper Hunter ring might sell well.
"I've got rare things on sale, stranger."
I'm wearing the armor now, so it doesn't take up inventory space, naturally.
You know, I want to combine the same type of gems.
With the hope that there's another Yellow Diamond somewhere...
So we just need to get Ashley...
Wow, there's so much treasure here!
Well, I want to believe she hasn't gone too far.

Did they get turned to stone?
You guys hear it from this side, right?
We have to go in from here?

"The voice of the wicked dwells in the flame,"
"Offer the crimson flame to the rightful seat."

Is that it, everyone? Nothing else?
In these battles, what is the

so I haven't been making Flash Grenades.

I guess I'll do some repairs.

Should I go back to the dorm?

"Next time, with the greeting you desire."
"Do you think I give up easily?"

Well, anyway, I don't really get it, but...

I didn't see it clearly but...
Can I go grab that Small Key?
I engaged in useless combat again.
to end up like this, but...

Let's do this! Where, where, where?

there'll be a chance to come back. Dunno. Feed him there too!
